Thanks @ebrevdo. Any pointers on how I can upgrade TF on the cloud TPU kernel to tf-nightly?
(When I use tfnightly on the VM only I see a binary incompatibility error since the cloud TPU kernel is running on TF1.9 and I cannot get that updated to tfnightly).
